ngerControl cim:PhaseTapChangerTabular cim:PhaseTapChangerLinear cim:PhaseTapChangerAsymmetrical cim:PhaseTapChangerSymmetrical cim:RatioTapChanger cim:ControlAreaGeneratingUnit cim:MutualCoupling cim:SubGeographicalRegion cim:MeasurementValueSource cim:GeographicalRegion cim:Season cim:BusNameMarker cim:FossilFuel cim:RatioTapChangerTable cim:DiscreteValue cim:AnalogValue cim:AccumulatorValue cim:StringMeasurementValue cim:DCNode cim:StringMeasurement cim:Analog cim:Accumulator cim:Discrete );
